{"tid":1723202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[給二號橋手足] 屌你明明成個文宣位，連BANNER都無條？！","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:41:18.000Z","uid":339797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cd065c8d13559ab9ad09e747a1711aadf1833e","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"入正題前我想搵兩個手足：<br />\n13號朝頭早喺2號橋分別問兩個手足借咗個尿袋同iphone線<br />\n借iphone線個手足仲話全家得佢用iphone叫我一定要還條線，結果你地去咗食早餐就再無見過你地so9sad<br />\n我想還野啊，見到個post搵一搵我丫唔該sosad<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rux5jBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRux5jBw.jpg&h=df4f439a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n喂今朝開返吐露港，車來車往<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但竟然連一條橫BANNER都無條？！<br />\n求其掛條底褲都大把人見到啦，唔係咁浪費啊嘛？！</span></span>"},{"pid":"06726d7b737ad99fe26f4f4e90bd5e12500d6725","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"a940efa970d9a8993cd2e61d050492c25f2ea390","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"001cacc1922a610f14d8bc46fe3e20cb551ba3dd","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"670432ad19819e6b7e41462668dd9fdcede3658f","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"4629dde8926dbb1d440a48ae584487ebfdcc279d","tid":1723202,"uid":265457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"有地利要用盡啊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e4e9c1cebcc83300419dd9ad4e6919639e6a0","tid":1723202,"uid":339797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"a35abe